{"tid":762040,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"三鹿前董事長因獄中表現積極三獲減刑","createTime":"2018-07-31T02:35:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-31T02:58:17.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8ec51753cc8970883b9b79483cda0b8f49a68cce","tid":762040,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T02:35:03.000Z","msg":"中國毒奶粉禍首獄中表現佳、3度獲減刑 網友諷說...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/business/page/800/2018/07/31/php0CYJRl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fbusiness%2Fpage%2F800%2F2018%2F07%2F31%2Fphp0CYJRl.jpg&h=ce29849a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2008年中國爆發毒奶粉事件，乳品大廠「三鹿集團」所生產的嬰兒奶粉，被發現含有三聚氰胺，最後引發一連串事件。（資料照，法新社）<br />\n<br />\n〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕2008年中國爆發毒奶粉事件，乳品大廠「三鹿集團」所生產的嬰兒奶粉，被發現含有三聚氰胺，最後引發一連串事件，三鹿集團前董事長田文華在2009年因此被判無期徒刑，不過事隔10年，田文華因在獄中表現良好，3度獲得減刑，導致她刑期在2027年就結束。<br />\n<br />\n不少中國網友對此事紛紛質疑：「是表現好，還是關係好？」、「果然人類的記性都不太好」、「這麼沒心沒肺的人坐幾年牢就出來了？」、「違法成本好低，我們能說什麼呢？」<br />\n<br />\n根據中國媒體《法制晚報》報導，田文華2009年1月22日被判無期徒刑、剝奪政治權利終身，之後被關進河北省女子監獄。<br />\n<br />\n不過河北省女子監獄在2011年提出減刑建議，指出田文華服刑時表現優異，有悔改表現，河北省高級人民法院審理後認為此言屬實，因此依法減刑，把田文華的刑期減為有期徒刑19年、剝奪政治權利6年（刑期至2030年11月3日）。這也是田文華的第1次減刑。<br />\n<br />\n到了2014年，河北省女子監獄指出，減刑後田文華表現良好，多次獲得記功、無違規違記，石家莊中級人民法院因此在2014年5月裁定，減去田文華1年9個月刑期、剝奪政治權利6年不變。此為田文華的第2次減刑。<br />\n<br />\n到了2016年7月，河北省女子監獄再度提出減刑建議，指出田文華服刑以來認罪悔罪，表現良好，經審理後，石家莊市冀中南地區人民檢察院對田文華的減刑沒有異議，因此法院裁定減去田文華1年6個月刑期、剝奪政治權利6年不變。此為田文華的第3次減刑。<br />\n<br />\n因此在經歷3次減刑後，田文華目前的刑期在2027年8月3日就結束了，與最一開始的無期徒刑相差甚大。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ec.ltn.com.tw/m/article/breakingnews/2504420\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2504420&d=ZwXxiz8aJHjnUpSvs3T%2F7sVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=953439f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2504420&h=358a7a9f\" target=\"_blank\">http://ec.ltn.com.tw/m/article/breakingnews/2504420</a>"},{"pid":"12df84fe91b3a2546db76a8494379696746a2b53","tid":762040,"uid":144735,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T02:39:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/103907_14597fdcb5764f905cd0d9082fce1185.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F31%2F103907_14597fdcb5764f905cd0d9082fce1185.jpg&h=870a0344&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e421c4df3b362db060592ccb3e4f8922b72c4e48","tid":762040,"uid":39628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"12df84fe91b3a2546db76a8494379696746a2b53","tid":762040,"uid":144735,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T02:39:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/103907_14597fdcb5764f905cd0d9082fce1185.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F31%2F103907_14597fdcb5764f905cd0d9082fce1185.jpg&h=870a0344&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T02:42:32.000Z","msg":"比左3次錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c5932cbf594b51d012fd5925b205b4042763e8d","tid":762040,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12df84fe91b3a2546db76a8494379696746a2b53","tid":762040,"uid":144735,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T02:39:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/103907_14597fdcb5764f905cd0d9082fce1185.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F31%2F103907_14597fdcb5764f905cd0d9082fce1185.jpg&h=870a0344&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T02:57:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c0bbc94e092821a7b1908d76ffa8de01f68263c","tid":762040,"uid":20241,"